a The normalized ultrafast photocurrent decay at various temperatures. The inset is decay constants dependence with temperature of region II and region III. Arrhenius plots at various times of region I (b), region II (c), and region III (d). e–g The corresponding thermal activation energy dependence in the 180–320 K temperature range with time.
